translations.title: 忍びよる未来

translations.description: Before they were brothers, Ace and Luffy lived in the mountains, dreaming of the day when they would take to the sea. In the criminal-infested junkyard known as Gray Terminal, Ace and his partner-in-crime Sabo robbed the thieves and scavengers.
translations.title: Gray Terminal

translations.description: Before they were brothers, Ace and Luffy lived in the mountains, dreaming of the day when they would take to the sea. In the criminal-infested junkyard known as Gray Terminal, Ace and his partner-in-crime Sabo robbed the thieves and scavengers.
translations.title: 不確かな物の終着駅 (グレイ・ターミナル)

translations.description: Ace, Sabo, and Luffy made a promise to one another over cups of sake that would shape their futures. Yet while the brothers' adventures continue, Sabo's unfortunate past catches up with him. Meanwhile, a horrific plot unfolds.
translations.title: Oath of Brotherhood

translations.description: Ace, Sabo, and Luffy made a promise to one another over cups of sake that would shape their futures. Yet while the brothers' adventures continue, Sabo's unfortunate past catches up with him. Meanwhile, a horrific plot unfolds.
translations.title: 兄弟盃 (volume) 兄弟杯 (magazine)

translations.description: Even as the fires in Gray Terminal threatened to consume them, Ace and Luffy fought Bluejam with all their might! In the wake of the tragedy, Sabo seized freedom in his hands and took to the sea, just as a Celestial Dragon arrived in High Town.
translations.title: Sabo's Sea

translations.description: Even as the fires in Gray Terminal threatened to consume them, Ace and Luffy fought Bluejam with all their might! In the wake of the tragedy, Sabo seized freedom in his hands and took to the sea, just as a Celestial Dragon arrived in High Town.
translations.title: サボの海

translations.description: Luffy and Ace buried their sorrow and grew stronger day by day as they trained to be pirates. Time marched on, and they eventually bade farewell to their childhood home and took to the sea, hoping to achieve the dream that Sabo could not.
translations.title: Will of the Winds

translations.description: Luffy and Ace buried their sorrow and grew stronger day by day as they trained to be pirates. Time marched on, and they eventually bade farewell to their childhood home and took to the sea, hoping to achieve the dream that Sabo could not.
translations.title: 風雲の志

translations.description: Determined to return to Sabaody and keep his promise to his crew, Luffy prepares for departure. However, when Dark King Rayleigh appears and makes him a surprising offer, Luffy is forced to make a decision that could alter the fate of his entire journey.
translations.title: Cheer

translations.title: エール

translations.description: Although Navy HQ is in ruins after the Summit War, marines and reporters still stalk its grounds. Luffy, Rayleigh, and Jinbe return to where Ace died to carry out a mysterious plan. If all goes well, Luffy’s crew will understand his actions.
translations.title: NEWS

translations.title: NEWS

translations.description: The Straw Hat Pirates have interpreted their captain's message to meet up again in two years. During this time, they will prepare themselves for the New World! In the Calm Belt, Luffy arrives in Luscaina to begin training under Rayleigh.
translations.title: 3D2Y

translations.title: 3D2Y

translations.description: The war has taken its toll on the world, and Luffy reminisces about younger days when he first met Ace and became his brother. To become strong enough to withstand the New World, Luffy must make a critical decision for himself and his crew.
translations.title: Post-War

translations.description: The war has taken its toll on the world, and Luffy reminisces about younger days when he first met Ace and became his brother. To become strong enough to withstand the New World, Luffy must make a critical decision for himself and his crew.
translations.title: Post-War

translations.description: Two years after the Summit War, the Straw Hat crew finally returns to Sabaody. However, the archipelago has changed, and with dangerous pirates lurking around in droves, their departure to the New World may not go as smoothly as hoped.
translations.title: بعد سنتين

translations.description: The mystery of Sanji's disappearance only deepens as Luffy learns that Big Mom’s lackeys caught up with him and offered him an invitation from one of the Four Emperors that simply could not be refused.

translations.description: Being separated from one of his crew is more than Luffy is willing to tolerate! The pirates make their way toward the nighttime ruler to find out more about their friend's disappearance.

translations.description: Zou cannot be reached by conventional means, nor is it easy to enter once one finds it. Within its secretive walls lie the mink tribe, and the Straw Hats soon discover that the people of Zou hold a piece of the puzzle that unlocks the mysteries of the world.

translations.description: Luffy's team—plus a stowaway—sets out from Zou on their way to win back Sanji. Meanwhile, the leading families and leaders of the world make their way to the Holy Land, Mary Geoise, for a pivotal round table conference.
translations.title: A World Abuzz

translations.description: El equipo de Luffy—más una polizona—parten de Zou directo a rescatar a Sanji. Mientras, las principales familias y líderes del mundo se abren paso a la Tierra Santa de Mary Geoise, para una vital conferencia de mesa redonda.

translations.description: Luffy's team—plus a stowaway—sets out from Zou on their way to win back Sanji. Meanwhile, the leading families and leaders of the world make their way to the Holy Land, Mary Geoise, for a pivotal round table conference.

translations.description: Without Sanji to properly identify safe and edible food, Luffy gets a stomach full of poisonous fish! With no antidotes on board, the Straw Hats must rely on a couple of mysterious—yet somehow familiar—passersby for help.
translations.title: 0 and 4

translations.description: Sin Sanji para identificar apropiadamente la comida segura y comestible, ¡Luffy se llena el estómago con pescado venenoso! Sin antídotos a bordo, los Sombrero de Paja deben confiar en un par de misteriosos—pero de alguna forma familiar—transeúntes por ayuda.
translations.title: 0 y 4

translations.description: Without Sanji to properly identify safe and edible food, Luffy gets a stomach full of poisonous fish! With no antidotes on board, the Straw Hats must rely on a couple of mysterious—yet somehow familiar—passersby for help.

translations.description: Arriving on Cacao Island, Luffy and Chopper are in heaven as everything before their eyes is edible. There, the Straw Hats encounter Sanji’s betrothed, Pudding, but when they challenge her for Sanji's heart, her answer is truly shocking.
translations.title: Totto Land

translations.description: Llegando a la Isla Cacao, Luffy y Chopper se sienten en el cielo, puesto que todo lo que está frente a sus ojos es comestible. Ahí, los Sombrero de Paja se encuentran con la comprometida, Pudding, pero cuando la desafían por el corazón de Sanji, su respuesta es realmente chocante.
translations.title: Totto Land

translations.description: Arriving on Cacao Island, Luffy and Chopper are in heaven as everything before their eyes is edible. There, the Straw Hats encounter Sanji’s betrothed, Pudding, but when they challenge her for Sanji's heart, her answer is truly shocking.
translations.title: トットランド

translations.description: Big Mom ravages Whole Cake Island in search of sweets, and while a familiar face across the waters has just what she needs, he also brings ill tidings. As the Straw Hats draw closer to the island, Pedro shares his sordid past in Big Mom’s territory.
translations.title: Pirate Emperor, Charlotte Linlin

translations.description: Big Mom causa estragos en Whole Cake Island en búsqueda de dulces, y mientras un rostro familiar cruzando el agua tiene justo lo que necesita, pero también trae malas noticias. A medida que los Sombrero de Paja se acercan a la isla, Pedro comparte su sórdido pasado en el territorio de Big Mom.
translations.title: Yonkou, Charlotte Linlin

translations.description: Big Mom ravages Whole Cake Island in search of sweets, and while a familiar face across the waters has just what she needs, he also brings ill tidings. As the Straw Hats draw closer to the island, Pedro shares his sordid past in Big Mom’s territory.

translations.description: Luffy’s group makes its way toward Sanji, only to be distracted by the endless supply of sweets and a second Luffy. Before they realize it, they are lost in the Seducing Woods! Meanwhile, Sanji confronts his older brother.
translations.title: Adventure in the Mysterious Forest

translations.description: El grupo de Luffy va en camino hacia Sanji, sólo para ser distraídos por la ilimitada cantidad de dulces y un segundo Luffy. Antes de que se den cuenta, ¡están perdidos el Bosque Seductor! Mientras, Sanji confronta a su hermano mayor.
translations.title: Aventura en el bosque misterioso

translations.description: Luffy’s group makes its way toward Sanji, only to be distracted by the endless supply of sweets and a second Luffy. Before they realize it, they are lost in the Seducing Woods! Meanwhile, Sanji confronts his older brother.
translations.title: 不思議な森の冒険

translations.description: Sanji faces his father in a duel as the wounds of his childhood are laid bare! Meanwhile, Luffy falls for the illusions of the forest, and Big Mom has Caesar at her whims, ready to use him to continue her maniacal pursuits.
translations.title: Vinsmoke Judge

translations.description: ¡Sanji se enfrenta a su padre en un duelo mientras las heridas de su infancia quedan al descubierto! Mientras tanto, Luffy cae en las ilusiones del bosque, y Big Mom tiene a Caesar para su antojo, lista para usarlo y continuar con sus maníacas actividades.

translations.title: Lola's Vivre Card

translations.description: El misterioso hombre medio enterrado revela su identidad, pero todo esto debe quedar de lado cuando uno de los comandantes más poderosos de Big Mom aparece. Las hazañas pasadas de Nami, sin embargo, tienen la llave para mantener a los malos a raya.

translations.description: The mysterious half-buried man comes clean about his identity, but this must all be put aside when one of Big Mom's most powerful commanders comes calling. Nami's past exploits, however, hold the key to keeping the baddies at bay.

translations.description: Luffy se enfrenta a un comandante de Big Mom, Charlotte Cracker, cuyos poderes van a ser más problemáticos de lo que puedan parecer. Mientras, Brook y Pedro se infiltran en Whole Cake Island y trabajan en un plan para evitar ser capturados.

translations.description: Luffy squares off against a commander of Big Mom, Charlotte Cracker, whose powers may prove more troublesome than they appear. Meanwhile, Brook and Pedro infiltrate Whole Cake Island and work out a plan to avoid getting caught.
translations.title: ルフィvs将星クラッカー

translations.description: Sanji challenges his entire family, but they have effectively ensured he follows their wedding scheme. The truth of Germa's power and Vinsmoke Judge’s dark history is also revealed. Meanwhile, Nami has recruited the homies and challenges Cracker!
translations.title: The Iron Mask

translations.description: Sanji desafía a su familia entera, pero ellos tienen una forma eficaz de asegurar que el matrimonio siga como planeado. La verdad detrás del poder del Germa y el oscuro pasado de Judge Vinsmoke también es revelado. Mientras, ¡Nami ha reclutado Homies y desafía a Cracker!

translations.description: Sanji challenges his entire family, but they have effectively ensured he follows their wedding scheme. The truth of Germa's power and Vinsmoke Judge’s dark history is also revealed. Meanwhile, Nami has recruited the homies and challenges Cracker!

translations.description: Sanji’s tragic history included a rare moment of compassion that was his only chance at escape, but even then, his father’s cruelty haunted him. In the present, Reiju helps Sanji straighten himself out before he meets with his fiancée.
translations.title: To the East Blue

translations.description: El pasado trágico de Sanji incluye un extraño momento de compasión que fue su única forma de escapar, pero incluso así, la crueldad de su padre lo atormenta. En el presente, Reiju endereza a Sanji antes de que conozca a su prometida.

translations.description: Sanji’s tragic history included a rare moment of compassion that was his only chance at escape, but even then, his father’s cruelty haunted him. In the present, Reiju helps Sanji straighten himself out before he meets with his fiancée.

translations.description: Luffy finishes off Cracker and finally catches up with Sanji, but the Straw Hats’ cook seems far from thrilled about the reunion. A heartbreaking duel commences, but a steadfast Luffy makes a solemn vow to his friend and crewmate.
translations.title: Luffy vs. Sanji

translations.description: Luffy derrota a Cracker y finalmente alcanza a Sanji, pero el cocinero de los Sombrero de Paja parece poco entusiasmado por la reunión. Un desgarrador duelo empieza, pero un firme Luffy hace un solemne voto a su amigo y tripulación.

translations.description: Luffy finishes off Cracker and finally catches up with Sanji, but the Straw Hats’ cook seems far from thrilled about the reunion. A heartbreaking duel commences, but a steadfast Luffy makes a solemn vow to his friend and crewmate.

translations.description: Luffy stands his ground and waits for Sanji to return, but as the vengeful army washes over him, only a true friend can step in to help. At Big Mom’s castle, Sanji and Pudding discuss their marriage and come to a startling conclusion!
translations.title: Forces of Rage

translations.description: Luffy mantiene su posición y espera al regreso de Sanji, pero un vengativo ejército lo aplasta, sólo un verdadero amigo puede intentar ayudarlo. En el castillo de Big Mom, ¡Sanji y Pudding discuten sobre su matrimonio y llegan a una sorprendente conclusión!

translations.description: Luffy stands his ground and waits for Sanji to return, but as the vengeful army washes over him, only a true friend can step in to help. At Big Mom’s castle, Sanji and Pudding discuss their marriage and come to a startling conclusion!

translations.description: Pedro creates a diversion for Brook to put his soulful plan into action. Meanwhile, the captured Luffy continues to goad Big Mom, and Pudding has the beginnings of rebellion stirring up inside her.
translations.title: Luffy and Big Mom

translations.description: Pedro crea una distracción para que Brook pueda poner su espirituoso plan en acción. Mientras, un Luffy capturado sigue provocando a Big Mom, y Pudding tiene una rebelión formándose dentro de ella.
translations.title: Luffy y Big Mom

translations.description: Pedro creates a diversion for Brook to put his soulful plan into action. Meanwhile, the captured Luffy continues to goad Big Mom, and Pudding has the beginnings of rebellion stirring up inside her.
translations.title: ルフィとビッグ・マム

translations.description: When Pudding arrives to meet the captured Luffy and Nami, their hopefulness suddenly turns to shock! To make matters worse, Brook comes face to face with Big Mom herself! At the risk of his own well-being, Luffy desperately tries to free himself.
translations.title: A Ray of Light

translations.description: Cuando Pudding llega a encontrarse con los capturados Luffy y Nami, ¡su esperanza pasa a ser una sorpresa! Para hacer las cosas peores, ¡Brook pasa a enfrentar cara a cara a Big Mom! Dispuesto a autoflagelarse, Luffy intenta desesperadamente escapar.
translations.title: Un rayo de luz

translations.description: When Pudding arrives to meet the captured Luffy and Nami, their hopefulness suddenly turns to shock! To make matters worse, Brook comes face to face with Big Mom herself! At the risk of his own well-being, Luffy desperately tries to free himself.
translations.title: 一筋の光

translations.description: Things are looking grim for Luffy and Nami until an unexpected ally appears. Elsewhere, Sanji confronts his sister about what Pudding plans to do and learns the powerful secret of their mother's undying love.
translations.title: Germa's Failure

translations.description: Las cosas parecen ser mortales para Luffy y Nami hasta que un aliado inesperado aparece. En otro lado, Sanji se enfrenta a su hermana con respecto a los planes de Pudding y aprende el secreto del amor incondicional de su madre.
translations.title: El fracaso de Germa

translations.description: Things are looking grim for Luffy and Nami until an unexpected ally appears. Elsewhere, Sanji confronts his sister about what Pudding plans to do and learns the powerful secret of their mother's undying love.
translations.title: ジェルマの失敗作

translations.description: Luffy fights through more obstacles in search of Sanji, and Brook hears Big Mom's plan firsthand as she shares her intentions with Pudding. While Big Mom's agents believe most of the Straw Hats to be under their control, Mont d'Or has his doubts.
translations.title: Not Here

translations.description: Luffy lucha contra más obstáculos en búsqueda de Sanji, y Brook escucha el plan de Big Mom de primera mano cuando esta le cuenta sus intenciones a Pudding. Mientras, los agentes de Big Mom creen que la mayoría de los Sombrero de Paja están bajo su control, pero Mont d'Or tiene sus dudas.
translations.title: No es aquí

translations.description: Luffy fights through more obstacles in search of Sanji, and Brook hears Big Mom's plan firsthand as she shares her intentions with Pudding. While Big Mom's agents believe most of the Straw Hats to be under their control, Mont d'Or has his doubts.
translations.title: ここじゃねェ

translations.description: Nami and co. finally locate Brook using the Mirro-world, but he is in the most inopportune of places! Meanwhile, Luffy is waylaid on his way back to the rendezvous, and Jinbe shares the awful truth about the wedding with the other Straw Hat pirates.
translations.title: Liar

translations.description: ¡Nami y compañía finalmente encuentran a Brook utilizando el Mundo Espejo, pero él está en una ubicación de lo más inoportuna! Mientras tanto, Luffy es emboscado antes de llegar al punto de encuentro prometido, y Jinbe comparte la terrible verdad sobre el matrimonio con los otros piratas del Sombrero de Paja.
translations.title: Mentiroso

translations.description: Nami and co. finally locate Brook using the Mirro-world, but he is in the most inopportune of places! Meanwhile, Luffy is waylaid on his way back to the rendezvous, and Jinbe shares the awful truth about the wedding with the other Straw Hat pirates.
translations.title: ウソつき

translations.description: Jinbe tells the Straw Hats about Capone “Gang” Bege and proposes a shocking plan to take down Big Mom! But before they are granted an audience with Bege, they must make themselves presentable.
translations.title: Rook

translations.description: Jinbe le cuenta a los Sombrero de Paja sobre Capone "Gang" Bege, ¡y propone un impactante plan para derrotar a Big Mom! Pero antes de poder tener una reunión con Bege, deben vestirse para la ocasión.
translations.title: Torre

translations.description: Jinbe tells the Straw Hats about Capone “Gang” Bege and proposes a shocking plan to take down Big Mom! But before they are granted an audience with Bege, they must make themselves presentable.
translations.title: ルーク

translations.description: The plan for Big Mom’s assassination is all set. Sanji heads back to his room to avoid suspicion, but Mont d’Or is hot on his trail. The day arrives, and guests from the criminal underground pour in in droves, some with their own agendas to settle.
translations.title: Emperor Assassination Plan

translations.description: El plan para el asesinato de Big Mom está listo. Sanji se devuelve a su habitación para evitar sospechas, pero Mont d'Or le sigue las huellas. El día llega, y los invitados del bajo mundo criminal aparecen por montones, algunos con sus propios planes para la ocasión.
translations.title: Plan para asesinar a una Yonkou

translations.description: The plan for Big Mom’s assassination is all set. Sanji heads back to his room to avoid suspicion, but Mont d’Or is hot on his trail. The day arrives, and guests from the criminal underground pour in in droves, some with their own agendas to settle.
translations.title: 四皇暗殺作戦

translations.description: Final preparations abound, plans come together, and Sanji meets his bride on the altar. As the veil is lifted off Pudding's face, emotions run high, and the chaos begins! As the proverbial icing on the cake, all hell breaks loose as Luffy charges in!
translations.title: Veteran Actor

translations.description: Los arreglos finales del plan están listos, y Sanji conoce a la novia en el altar. Mientras el velo es sacado de la cara de Pudding, ¡los sentimientos se aceleran y el caos comienza! ¡Como la guinda del pastel, el infierno se desata cuando Luffy salta a la carga!

translations.description: Final preparations abound, plans come together, and Sanji meets his bride on the altar. As the veil is lifted off Pudding's face, emotions run high, and the chaos begins! As the proverbial icing on the cake, all hell breaks loose as Luffy charges in!
translations.title: 演技派

translations.description: The wedding and the precious cake crumble to pieces around Big Mom as a slew of Luffys wreak havoc. The chaos pushes Big Mom past the edge of sanity, so her children make a move against Germa while Pudding takes aim at Sanji.
translations.title: The Honorable

translations.description: El matrimonio y el precioso pastel se derrumban en pedazos alrededor de Big Mom como los estragos que está provocando Luffy. El caos hace que Big Mom sea empujada más allá del borde de la sanidad mental, por lo que sus hijos hacen una jugada contra el Germa mientras Pudding apunta a Sanji.
translations.title: El caballero consumado

translations.description: The wedding and the precious cake crumble to pieces around Big Mom as a slew of Luffys wreak havoc. The chaos pushes Big Mom past the edge of sanity, so her children make a move against Germa while Pudding takes aim at Sanji.
translations.title: 義侠派

translations.description: Luffy dashes toward Big Mom to show her the broken portrait again, and Sanji attempts to free his family. Here, Big Mom’s tragic and sad history is revealed: from the very beginning, Big Mom's voracious hunger has brought her into conflict with others.
translations.title: Hey, Mother

translations.description: Luffy se lanza hacia Big Mom para mostrarle de nuevo el retrato roto, y Sanji intenta liberar a su familia. Se revela la trágica y triste historia de Big Mom: desde el principio, el hambre voraz de Big Mom la ha puesto en conflicto con los demás.
translations.title: Hey, Madre

translations.description: Luffy dashes toward Big Mom to show her the broken portrait again, and Sanji attempts to free his family. Here, Big Mom’s tragic and sad history is revealed: from the very beginning, Big Mom's voracious hunger has brought her into conflict with others.
translations.title: ねぇマザー

translations.description: A young Linlin managed to enrage the giants of Elbaf, but Mother Carmel begged for clemency on her behalf. After Carmel’s mysterious disappearance, Linlin fell in with a new cohort and found her reason to go on living.
translations.title: HAPPY BIRTHDAY

translations.description: Una joven Linlin consiguió enfurecer a los gigantes de Elbaf, pero Mother Carmel pidió clemencia en su nombre. Tras la misteriosa desaparición de Carmel, Linlin se unió a una nueva comunidad y encontró su razón para seguir viviendo.
translations.title: Feliz cumpleaños

translations.description: A young Linlin managed to enrage the giants of Elbaf, but Mother Carmel begged for clemency on her behalf. After Carmel’s mysterious disappearance, Linlin fell in with a new cohort and found her reason to go on living.
translations.title: HAPPY BIRTHDAY

translations.description: The Straw Hats and Germa 66 become cornered in Bege's stronghold, and the full might of the Big Mom Pirates is pinning them down! It is only a matter of time before their defenses crack, so they take the only way out and make a break for it.
translations.title: Under Siege

translations.description: Los Sombrero de Paja y Germa 66 están acorralados en la fortaleza de Bege, ¡y todo el poder de los Piratas de Big Mom los está acorralando! Es sólo cuestión de tiempo que sus defensas se resquebrajen, así que toman la única vía de escape, y huyen.
translations.title: Bajo asedio

translations.description: The Straw Hats and Germa 66 become cornered in Bege's stronghold, and the full might of the Big Mom Pirates is pinning them down! It is only a matter of time before their defenses crack, so they take the only way out and make a break for it.
translations.title: 籠城

translations.description: Caesar flies the entire alliance, still inside Bege, out of the venue! However, the full might of the Big Mom Pirates proves too much. The alliance’s annihilation is imminent, but something shakes the playing field.
translations.title: You Can Do It, Caesar!!

translations.description: Caesar hace volar a toda la alianza, aún dentro de Bege, fuera del recinto. Sin embargo, todo el poder de los Piratas de Big Mom es demasiado. La destrucción de la alianza es inminente, pero algo sacude el campo de juego.
translations.title: ¡¡Vamos, Caesar!!

translations.description: Caesar flies the entire alliance, still inside Bege, out of the venue! However, the full might of the Big Mom Pirates proves too much. The alliance’s annihilation is imminent, but something shakes the playing field.
translations.title: がんばれシーザー!!

translations.description: The Straw Hats continue their mad dash to the Sunny, and Pudding puts her plan to rebuild the cake into action. As Zeus pursues the Straw Hats, Nami keeps him occupied with a shocking surprise that might stop Big Mom in her tracks!
translations.title: Become My Servant

translations.description: Los Sombrero de Paja continúan su loca carrera hacia el Sunny, y Pudding pone en marcha su plan para rehacer el pastel. Mientras Zeus persigue a los Sombrero de Paja, ¡Nami lo mantiene ocupado con una impactante sorpresa que podría detener a Big Mom!
translations.title: A cambio sé mi sirviente

translations.description: The Straw Hats continue their mad dash to the Sunny, and Pudding puts her plan to rebuild the cake into action. As Zeus pursues the Straw Hats, Nami keeps him occupied with a shocking surprise that might stop Big Mom in her tracks!
translations.title: 私のしもべになりなさい

translations.description: Big Mom is relentless in her pursuit of the Straw Hats. Elsewhere, the plan to recreate the wedding cake progresses while Pudding’s unpredictable heart confuses everyone, including herself.
translations.title: A Woman's Honor

translations.description: Big Mom es implacable en su persecución a los Sombrero de Paja. En otro lugar, el plan para recrear el pastel de bodas progresa mientras el impredecible corazón de Pudding confunde a todos, incluida ella misma.
translations.title: El honor de una mujer

translations.description: Big Mom is relentless in her pursuit of the Straw Hats. Elsewhere, the plan to recreate the wedding cake progresses while Pudding’s unpredictable heart confuses everyone, including herself.
translations.title: 女の仁義

translations.description: Sandwiched between Big Mom and her advancing fleet, the only hope left to the Sunny is to blast right through it all. Meanwhile, Pedro comes face-to-face with his past and does what he must to ensure the success of his friends.
translations.title: Mink Pedro, Captain of the Guardians

translations.description: Atrapados entre Big Mom y su flota, la única esperanza que le queda al Sunny es volar sobre todo. Mientras tanto, Pedro se enfrenta a su pasado y hace lo que debe para asegurar el éxito de sus amigos.
translations.title: Tribu Mink, el jefe de los guardianes, Pedro

translations.description: Sandwiched between Big Mom and her advancing fleet, the only hope left to the Sunny is to blast right through it all. Meanwhile, Pedro comes face-to-face with his past and does what he must to ensure the success of his friends.
translations.title: ミンク族 侠客団団長ペドロ

translations.description: In the Mirro-world, Luffy confronts the formidable Charlotte Katakuri, Big Mom’s strongest child. Meanwhile, Pudding and Sanji arrive at Cacao Island to remake the cake, but they bicker like a married couple the whole time.
translations.title: Zero Escape

translations.description: En el Mundo Espejo, Luffy se enfrenta al temible Charlotte Katakuri, el hijo más fuerte de Big Mom. Mientras tanto, Pudding y Sanji llegan a la Isla Cacao para rehacer el pastel, pero discuten como un matrimonio todo el tiempo.
translations.title: Sin salida

translations.description: In the Mirro-world, Luffy confronts the formidable Charlotte Katakuri, Big Mom’s strongest child. Meanwhile, Pudding and Sanji arrive at Cacao Island to remake the cake, but they bicker like a married couple the whole time.
translations.title: 退路0

translations.description: Nami and Luffy discuss a rendezvous point while the others break the mirrors on the Sunny. Little do they know their plan is overheard, and Luffy’s grueling battle against Katakuri—haki vs. haki, rubber vs. mochi—intensifies.
translations.title: Wave Room

translations.description: Nami y Luffy discuten un punto de encuentro mientras los demás rompen los espejos del Sunny. Lo que no saben es que su plan es escuchado, y la agotadora batalla de Luffy contra Katakuri, de Haki contra Haki y goma contra mochi, se intensifica.
translations.title: Habitación de olas

translations.description: Nami and Luffy discuss a rendezvous point while the others break the mirrors on the Sunny. Little do they know their plan is overheard, and Luffy’s grueling battle against Katakuri—haki vs. haki, rubber vs. mochi—intensifies.
translations.title: 波の部屋

translations.description: Katakuri retires to his sanctuary to enjoy a merienda—a sweet chance to replenish his haki! But he is not the only one munching away. A mochi mountain has crushed Luffy, and he has found a delectable way to escape.
translations.title: Merienda

translations.description: Katakuri se retira a su santuario para disfrutar de una merienda, ¡una dulce oportunidad para reponer su Haki! Pero no es el único que está comiendo. Una montaña de mochi ha aplastado a Luffy, y este ha encontrado una deliciosa forma de escapar.
translations.title: Merienda

translations.description: Katakuri retires to his sanctuary to enjoy a merienda—a sweet chance to replenish his haki! But he is not the only one munching away. A mochi mountain has crushed Luffy, and he has found a delectable way to escape.
translations.title: おやつの時間

translations.description: When Chiffon comes under attack, Sanji must choose between defending her or revealing his whereabouts to his enemies. Elsewhere, Luffy uses Charlotte Brûlée as a human shield to avoid the wrath of Big Mom.
translations.title: Way of Life

translations.description: Chiffon es víctima de un ataque, y Sanji debe elegir entre defenderla o revelar su paradero a sus enemigos. En otro lugar, Luffy utiliza a Charlotte Brûlée como escudo humano para evitar la ira de Big Mom.
translations.title: Ese es mi estilo de vida

translations.description: When Chiffon comes under attack, Sanji must choose between defending her or revealing his whereabouts to his enemies. Elsewhere, Luffy uses Charlotte Brûlée as a human shield to avoid the wrath of Big Mom.
translations.title: 生き様でちゅよ

translations.description: Sanji and Bege contend with Charlotte Oven, who boils the sea itself! Meanwhile, a vicious pincer attack bears down on the Straw Hats, but Carrot draws on a deep power within and springs to action under the light of the full moon.
translations.title: Lion

translations.description: ¡Sanji y Bege se enfrentan a Charlotte Oven, quien hierve el propio mar! Mientras tanto, un feroz ataque de pinzas se cierne sobre los Sombrero de Paja, pero Carrot recurre a un profundo poder interior y entra en acción bajo la luz de la luna llena.
translations.title: León

translations.description: Sanji and Bege contend with Charlotte Oven, who boils the sea itself! Meanwhile, a vicious pincer attack bears down on the Straw Hats, but Carrot draws on a deep power within and springs to action under the light of the full moon.
translations.title: 獅子

translations.description: Wielding Napoleon and backed by Zeus and Prometheus, Big Mom wreaks havoc on the Sunny. As the Straw Hats try to kick out the emperor, their ship catches fire! But then, Jinbe steps up to the plate to take a swing.
translations.title: Unknown Mama

translations.description: Empuñando a Napoleón y con el apoyo de Zeus y Prometeo, Big Mom causa estragos en el Sunny. Mientras los Sombrero de Paja intentan echar a la Yonkou, su barco se incendia. Pero entonces, Jinbe se acerca al escenario para dar un golpe.
translations.title: Mamá desconocida

translations.description: Wielding Napoleon and backed by Zeus and Prometheus, Big Mom wreaks havoc on the Sunny. As the Straw Hats try to kick out the emperor, their ship catches fire! But then, Jinbe steps up to the plate to take a swing.
translations.title: 未知のママ

translations.description: The cake is finally brought before Big Mom. With the end of her vicious rampage in sight, the Straw Hats may just get their chance to flee! Big Mom's crew is forced to decide who to attack, and Luffy grows ever closer to mastering his haki.
translations.title: They Believe in Me

translations.description: El pastel es finalmente llevado ante Big Mom. Dando así fin a sus incesantes ataques, ¡los Sombrero de Paja podrían tener la oportunidad de huir! La tripulación de Big Mom se ve obligada a decidir a quién atacar, y Luffy está cada vez más cerca de perfeccionar su Haki.
translations.title: ¡Confían en mí!

translations.description: The cake is finally brought before Big Mom. With the end of her vicious rampage in sight, the Straw Hats may just get their chance to flee! Big Mom's crew is forced to decide who to attack, and Luffy grows ever closer to mastering his haki.
translations.title: 信じられてる

translations.description: Desiring revenge after complete embarrassment, Big Mom’s children band together to smash the Straw Hats. Meanwhile, Luffy and Katakuri are locked in a duel to end all duels, where each blow could be the last.
translations.title: Pirate Luffy vs. Commander Katakuri

translations.description: Deseando vengarse después de la vergüenza total que vivieron, los hijos de Big Mom se unen para aplastar a los Sombrero de Paja. Mientras tanto, Luffy y Katakuri se enfrentan en un duelo para acabar con todos los duelos, donde cada golpe podría ser el último.
translations.title: El pirata Luffy vs. el general dulce, Katakuri

translations.description: Desiring revenge after complete embarrassment, Big Mom’s children band together to smash the Straw Hats. Meanwhile, Luffy and Katakuri are locked in a duel to end all duels, where each blow could be the last.
translations.title: 海賊ルフィVS将星カタクリ

translations.description: Luffy's dramatic battle finally draws to a close, and a whole host of the Big Mom Pirates watch the last mirror to see who will come through.
translations.title: One Last Thing

translations.description: La dramática batalla de Luffy finalmente acaba, y todos los Piratas de Big Mom observan el último espejo para ver quién sale victorioso.
translations.title: La última petición

translations.description: Luffy's dramatic battle finally draws to a close, and a whole host of the Big Mom Pirates watch the last mirror to see who will come through.
translations.title: 最後のお願い

translations.description: Sanji tries his best to save himself and his captain. Now, the fate of Totto Land rests on the taste of the wedding cake! With the help of Germa and the Sun Pirates, the Straw Hats see their chance to escape!
translations.title: BAD END MUSICAL

translations.description: Sanji hace todo lo posible por salvarse a sí mismo y a su capitán. ¡Ahora, el destino de Totto Land depende del sabor del pastel de bodas! Con la ayuda de Germa y los Piratas del Sol, los Sombrero de Paja ven su oportunidad de escapar.
translations.title: Musical con final terrible

translations.description: Sanji tries his best to save himself and his captain. Now, the fate of Totto Land rests on the taste of the wedding cake! With the help of Germa and the Sun Pirates, the Straw Hats see their chance to escape!
translations.title: BAD END MUSICAL

translations.description: As the Big Mom Pirate fleet approaches, Jinbe makes a crucial decision. At a great cost of energy and life, the Straw Hats make it out of Totto Land. Left behind in their wake are allies, friends, and would-be lovers.
translations.title: END ROLL

translations.description: Mientras la flota de Big Mom se acerca, Jinbe toma una decisión crucial. Con un gran coste de energía y vida, los Sombrero de Paja consiguen escapar de Totto Land. Tras ellos, quedan aliados, amigos y posibles amantes.
translations.title: Rodaje final

translations.description: As the Big Mom Pirate fleet approaches, Jinbe makes a crucial decision. At a great cost of energy and life, the Straw Hats make it out of Totto Land. Left behind in their wake are allies, friends, and would-be lovers.
translations.title: END ROLL

translations.description: Luffy will not sail the seas without his cook, so he stubbornly goes after Sanji to Whole Cake Island. However, knocking on an emperor's door is easier said than done.
translations.title: Whole Cake Island

translations.description: Luffy no se irá al mar sin su cocinero, así que testarudamente va tras Sanji hacia Whole Cake Island. Sin embargo, golpear la puerta de un Yonkou es algo más fácil de decir que hacer.
translations.title: Whole Cake Island

translations.description: Luffy will not sail the seas without his cook, so he stubbornly goes after Sanji to Whole Cake Island. However, knocking on an emperor's door is easier said than done.
translations.title: ホールケーキアイランド編

translations.description: Luffy’s reputation grows as all eyes look toward the Straw Hats’ next move. Meanwhile, the royals of the world make their way to the Reverie, but their absence welcomes a raid by a vicious band of pirates on the Kingdom of Lulucia.
translations.title: The Fifth Emperor

translations.description: Luffy’s reputation grows as all eyes look toward the Straw Hats’ next move. Meanwhile, the royals of the world make their way to the Reverie, but their absence welcomes a raid by a vicious band of pirates on the Kingdom of Lulucia.
translations.title: 5番目の皇帝

translations.description: At New Marineford, Fleet Admiral Sakazuki hears the news about Luffy while nobles from around the world gather for the Reverie! At the Red Line, Garp is escorting King Neptune’s family when Shirahoshi sees the surface world for the first time.
translations.title: A Beautiful World

translations.description: At New Marineford, Fleet Admiral Sakazuki hears the news about Luffy while nobles from around the world gather for the Reverie! At the Red Line, Garp is escorting King Neptune’s family when Shirahoshi sees the surface world for the first time.
translations.title: 美しい世界

translations.description: As the Reverie commences, Emperors Big Mom and Kaido both set their sights on Luffy! Meanwhile, a mysterious outsider visits the highest authority in the world, and the Revolutionary Army confirms its desire to save Kuma.
translations.title: The Empty Throne

translations.description: As the Reverie commences, Emperors Big Mom and Kaido both set their sights on Luffy! Meanwhile, a mysterious outsider visits the highest authority in the world, and the Revolutionary Army confirms its desire to save Kuma.
translations.title: 虚の玉座

translations.description: Every four years, the leaders of the world gather at the Holy Land to discuss a mutually agreed upon path for the government. During this particular Reverie, many parties with their own agendas arrive... and some are uninvited.
translations.title: Reverie

translations.description: Every four years, the leaders of the world gather at the Holy Land to discuss a mutually agreed upon path for the government. During this particular Reverie, many parties with their own agendas arrive... and some are uninvited.
translations.title: 世界会議

translations.description: Luffy and the others see familiar faces in a newspaper article about the Reverie right as they approach Wano. However, this dangerous and foreboding land is as inaccessible as it is mysterious, with the sea itself acting as a barrier!
translations.title: Onward to Wano

translations.description: Luffy and the others see familiar faces in a newspaper article about the Reverie right as they approach Wano. However, this dangerous and foreboding land is as inaccessible as it is mysterious, with the sea itself acting as a barrier!
translations.title: いざワノ国へ

translations.description: A mysterious country, a rampaging slasher, an ancient samurai ritual of seppuku—and Zoro in the crosshairs! Stranded alone on the beach, Luffy tries to gather his bearings only to be confronted by some dangerous local fauna.
translations.title: Seppuku

translations.description: A mysterious country, a rampaging slasher, an ancient samurai ritual of seppuku—and Zoro in the crosshairs! Stranded alone on the beach, Luffy tries to gather his bearings only to be confronted by some dangerous local fauna.
translations.title: 切腹

translations.description: Otama recounts her promise to Ace while Luffy rushes her to medical attention. But just as they reach the wasteland, a familiar face comes into view, and Kaido's underlings show up, too!
translations.title: Amigasa Village

translations.description: Otama recounts her promise to Ace while Luffy rushes her to medical attention. But just as they reach the wasteland, a familiar face comes into view, and Kaido's underlings show up, too!
translations.title: 編笠村

translations.description: Luffy and Zoro are stalled by Hawkins, but their fortune looks bright when a woman guides them to a teahouse. There, they find an herbal remedy for the river poison that Otama drank, while old acquaintances look on from a distance.
translations.title: Tsuru Returns the Favor

translations.description: Luffy and Zoro are stalled by Hawkins, but their fortune looks bright when a woman guides them to a teahouse. There, they find an herbal remedy for the river poison that Otama drank, while old acquaintances look on from a distance.
translations.title: 鶴の恩返し

translations.description: Otama is kidnapped by Kaido’s gifters and taken to a flourishing settlement called Bakura Town where a creepy-looking headliner was expecting her. Luffy, Zoro, and the samurai Okiku rush to her rescue.
translations.title: Okobore Town

translations.description: Otama is kidnapped by Kaido’s gifters and taken to a flourishing settlement called Bakura Town where a creepy-looking headliner was expecting her. Luffy, Zoro, and the samurai Okiku rush to her rescue.
translations.title: おこぼれ町

translations.description: Luffy challenges Urashima, the strongest yokozuna in Wano, to a sumo match! However, Urashima is willing to resort to illegal moves. Meanwhile, Holdem tells Otama that he must punish her for a crime she committed.
translations.title: Wano's Grand Sumo Tournament

translations.description: Luffy challenges Urashima, the strongest yokozuna in Wano, to a sumo match! However, Urashima is willing to resort to illegal moves. Meanwhile, Holdem tells Otama that he must punish her for a crime she committed.
translations.title: ワノ国大相撲

translations.description: Luffy and co. finally find Otama hanging from the mouth of a lion in Holdem’s stomach. Luffy prepares to save Otama from Kaido’s lackey, and elsewhere, a mysterious figure confronts Basil Hawkins.
translations.title: The Provisions Ship

translations.description: Luffy and co. finally find Otama hanging from the mouth of a lion in Holdem’s stomach. Luffy prepares to save Otama from Kaido’s lackey, and elsewhere, a mysterious figure confronts Basil Hawkins.
translations.title: 食糧宝船

translations.description: Zoro and the others dash out of Bakura Town on the treasure ship filled with food! Luffy catches up to them, and together, they distribute food and water to the people of Okobore Town. Later, Law takes them to the ruins of a hilltop castle.
translations.title: The Ruins of Oden Castle

translations.description: Zoro and the others dash out of Bakura Town on the treasure ship filled with food! Luffy catches up to them, and together, they distribute food and water to the people of Okobore Town. Later, Law takes them to the ruins of a hilltop castle.
translations.title: おでん城跡

translations.description: Kin’emon tells Luffy and the others about how Kozuki Oden brought peace to Kuri and became its daimyo. However, he was set up by Kaido and Orochi. When Kin’emon ran to save Oden’s wife, she revealed a shocking truth.
translations.title: I Love Oden

translations.description: Kin’emon tells Luffy and the others about how Kozuki Oden brought peace to Kuri and became its daimyo. However, he was set up by Kaido and Orochi. When Kin’emon ran to save Oden’s wife, she revealed a shocking truth.
translations.title: おでんが好き

translations.description: Ashura Doji, a.k.a Shutenmaru, is one of the allies Kin’emon wants to search for, and he leads a raid on Okobore Town to steal the food that Luffy brought. This unrest prompts the drunken Kaido to fly above Okobore Town in his dragon form.
translations.title: Shutenmaru

translations.description: Ashura Doji, a.k.a Shutenmaru, is one of the allies Kin’emon wants to search for, and he leads a raid on Okobore Town to steal the food that Luffy brought. This unrest prompts the drunken Kaido to fly above Okobore Town in his dragon form.
translations.title: 酒天丸

translations.description: Infuriated by Kaido’s violence toward his allies, Luffy lands blow after blow on the drunken emperor. When he activates Gear Fourth and launches even more powerful attacks, Kaido fights back. Law tries to rescue Luffy but is interrupted by Hawkins.
translations.title: Emperor Kaido vs. Luffy

translations.description: Infuriated by Kaido’s violence toward his allies, Luffy lands blow after blow on the drunken emperor. When he activates Gear Fourth and launches even more powerful attacks, Kaido fights back. Law tries to rescue Luffy but is interrupted by Hawkins.
translations.title: 四皇カイドウVSルフィ

translations.description: Luffy is sent to a great mine where prisoners must endure harsh, forced labor. There, he has an unexpected reunion. Meanwhile, Okiku rushes to the ruins of Oden Castle to confirm the safety of the Straw Hats and the others.
translations.title: Hah

translations.description: Luffy is sent to a great mine where prisoners must endure harsh, forced labor. There, he has an unexpected reunion. Meanwhile, Okiku rushes to the ruins of Oden Castle to confirm the safety of the Straw Hats and the others.
translations.title: は

translations.description: Perona prepares to leave Gloom Island after she finds out that her captain, Gecko Moria, is still alive. Meanwhile, Moria raids the island Hachinosu with his zombie army to retrieve his old friend from Blackbeard.
translations.title: Void

translations.description: Perona prepares to leave Gloom Island after she finds out that her captain, Gecko Moria, is still alive. Meanwhile, Moria raids the island Hachinosu with his zombie army to retrieve his old friend from Blackbeard.
translations.title: ブランク

translations.description: In the Prisoner Mining Camp, Luffy’s and Kid’s competition garners the wrong kind of attention. Meanwhile, Sanji’s soba becomes immensely popular, but gang members disturb his business and knock over a customer’s bowl.
translations.title: Otoko the Kamuro

translations.description: In the Prisoner Mining Camp, Luffy’s and Kid’s competition garners the wrong kind of attention. Meanwhile, Sanji’s soba becomes immensely popular, but gang members disturb his business and knock over a customer’s bowl.
translations.title: 禿のおトコ

translations.description: Wano’s top courtesan Komurasaki is in procession and slowly makes her way to Orochi Palace. Sanji and the others are among a crowd on the street. While everyone is fascinated by the oiran, some seeking vengeance get in her way.
translations.title: Oiran Komurasaki Arrives

translations.description: Wano’s top courtesan Komurasaki is in procession and slowly makes her way to Orochi Palace. Sanji and the others are among a crowd on the street. While everyone is fascinated by the oiran, some seeking vengeance get in her way.
translations.title: 花魁小紫登場

translations.description: In the Flower Capital, a member of the Beast Pirates, Page One, attacks every soba restaurant in the city in search of Sanji. The Straw Hat’s cook faces Kaido’s headliner while using Germa’s device for the first time to hide his identity.
translations.title: Soba Mask

translations.description: In the Flower Capital, a member of the Beast Pirates, Page One, attacks every soba restaurant in the city in search of Sanji. The Straw Hat’s cook faces Kaido’s headliner while using Germa’s device for the first time to hide his identity.
translations.title: おそばマスク

translations.description: At the shogun’s banquet, the oiran’s child attendant Otoko bursts with laughter and cannot stop. The enraged Shogun Orochi attacks her, but an unexpected person stands in his way. To end the to-do, Kyoshiro takes matters into his own hands.
translations.title: The Shogun and the Oiran

translations.description: At the shogun’s banquet, the oiran’s child attendant Otoko bursts with laughter and cannot stop. The enraged Shogun Orochi attacks her, but an unexpected person stands in his way. To end the to-do, Kyoshiro takes matters into his own hands.
translations.title: 将軍と花魁

translations.description: Chopper’s group is off to rescue Luffy from the Prisoner Mining Camp, but the Straw Hat captain is in a bit of a bind. While Luffy tries to save old man Hyo from execution, Queen the Plague comes to visit the prison.
translations.title: Hyogoro the Flower

translations.description: Chopper’s group is off to rescue Luffy from the Prisoner Mining Camp, but the Straw Hat captain is in a bit of a bind. While Luffy tries to save old man Hyo from execution, Queen the Plague comes to visit the prison.
translations.title: 花のヒョウ五郎

translations.description: Luffy fights in an endless sumo match to protect old man Hyo, and Nami, Robin, and Shinobu are cornered as Hawkins raids the bathhouse. Elsewhere, Zoro faces a samurai who accuses him of stealing Shusui, but their duel is interrupted by a woman’s scream.
translations.title: Gyukimaru of Oihagi Bridge

translations.description: Luffy fights in an endless sumo match to protect old man Hyo, and Nami, Robin, and Shinobu are cornered as Hawkins raids the bathhouse. Elsewhere, Zoro faces a samurai who accuses him of stealing Shusui, but their duel is interrupted by a woman’s scream.
translations.title: おいはぎ橋の牛鬼丸

translations.description: The wounded Zoro wakes up to find out the shocking identity of the woman he saved and is told the unbelievable tale of 20 years earlier. Meanwhile, Luffy’s “training” is not getting anywhere, but a surprising person gives him his first lesson.
translations.title: A Woman's Secret

translations.description: The wounded Zoro wakes up to find out the shocking identity of the woman he saved and is told the unbelievable tale of 20 years earlier. Meanwhile, Luffy’s “training” is not getting anywhere, but a surprising person gives him his first lesson.
translations.title: 女の秘密

translations.description: The smiling man Tonoyasu leaves all who met him mystified, what with his familiar terms of address and his shocking knowledge of the rebellion. In Udon prison, Luffy continues his new haki training, and during a brief respite, Raizo appears before him.
translations.title: Sparks of Rebellion

translations.description: The smiling man Tonoyasu leaves all who met him mystified, what with his familiar terms of address and his shocking knowledge of the rebellion. In Udon prison, Luffy continues his new haki training, and during a brief respite, Raizo appears before him.
translations.title: 反逆の火種
